  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/industry/\" rel=\"tag\">产业新闻</a></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/05/27/apple-may-enter-the-smart-home-business/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://o.aolcdn.com/hss/storage/midas/7467cd31ef0f5d7c5c2ae79f93d5ac9a/200166240/IMG_6677.jpg\" /></a></div>\n<br />\n先别管<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/02/03/apple-wearable-inductive-charging/\">智慧型手表</a>了，你有听说 Apple 将可能进军智慧型家电产品的领域吗？是说，Apple 与 Google 两间公司还真的是死对头呢，前不久<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/02/12/google-completes-nest-acquisition/\">后者才收购了 Nest</a>，现在，Apple 传出将不甘示弱地推出自有的智慧家电产品。根据 Financial Times 的消息来源指出，Apple 将在次周的 WWDC 上首度推出他们的 Smart Home 平台，将智能家居产品协作融入自有的 iOS 系统当中。假如成真的话，看来今年度两间公司要玩的梗应该就是这块领域了吧？（Siri 表示：帮你导航<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2012/09/28/tim-cook-apologizes-for-maps-mess/\"><s>搞砸</s></a>就算了，现在还要请我管家了吗！）<br />\n<br />\n经由：<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2014/05/26/apple-may-enter-the-smart-home-business/\">Engadget</a><br />\n引用来源：<a href=\"http://www.ft.com/intl/cms/s/0/1bef71b8-e433-11e3-a73a-00144feabdc0.html?siteedition=intl#axzz32pqFcelV\">Financial Times</a><p><h6 style=\"clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"></h6><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/05/27/apple-may-enter-the-smart-home-business/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent link to this entry\">此文章网址</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/forward/20892912/\" title=\"Send this entry to a friend via email\">转寄此文章</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/05/27/apple-may-enter-the-smart-home-business/#comments\" title=\"View reader comments on this entry\">回应</a><hr size=\"1\" />", 
